  "content": "<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n        <p>Los Angeles offers countless options for cosmetic dentistry, which makes choosing the right practice feel challenging. Focus on three essentials: expertise, technology, and comfort.</p>\n        <p>First, review each dentist’s training and case work. Experienced cosmetic dentists openly share before-and-after photos, explain their approach to veneers, bonding, whitening, and Invisalign, and welcome your questions about bite design and long-term results.</p>\n        <p>Next, look for modern technology. Digital scanners, 3D smile previews, and laser whitening tools help ensure precise, comfortable care. Advanced equipment reduces guesswork and lets you see what your new smile will look like before treatment begins.</p>\n        <p>Finally, consider how the office makes you feel. A calm environment, friendly team, and thoughtful amenities turn appointments into a positive experience—especially when treatments require multiple visits.</p>\n        <p>If you want to explore your options, schedule a consultation with our West Hollywood team. We combine spa-level comfort with award-winning cosmetic dentistry so you can enjoy every step toward your refreshed smile.</p>\n      </div>",
