  "excerpt": "Hollywood veneers are thin porcelain shells that brighten, straighten, and reshape your smile.  They cover the front of your teeth to hide stains, chips, uneven edges, and small gaps while still looking natural in photos and everyday life.",
  "content": "<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n        <p>Hollywood veneers are thin porcelain shells that brighten, straighten, and reshape your smile. They cover the front of your teeth to hide stains, chips, uneven edges, and small gaps while still looking natural in photos and everyday life.</p>\n        <p>The process is simple. After a consultation, we take digital scans, design your ideal tooth shape and shade, and place temporary veneers so you can preview the look. When the custom porcelain arrives, we bond each veneer securely and polish the finish so it blends seamlessly.</p>\n        <p>Veneers are perfect if you want a camera-ready smile without braces or repeated whitening. They are durable, stain-resistant, and can last a decade or more with regular brushing, flossing, and professional cleanings.</p>\n        <p>Ready to see how veneers could elevate your smile? Visit our West Hollywood office for a relaxed consultation. We will walk you through options, share inspiring before-and-after photos, and design a plan tailored to your goals.</p>\n        <h2>You’ve got Hollywood</h2>\n        <p>style , but do you have a Hollywood smile? That’s what porcelain veneers can do for you. Hollywood-style veneers can correct discolored or misshapen teeth to totally transform your smile.</p>\n        <h2>What are Hollywood Porcelain Veneers?</h2>\n        <p>Veneers are a super-thin layer of porcelain that are gently bonded to the front of your teeth. They can be applied in as few as three dentist visits. When you work with a world-class cosmetic dentist like Exquisite Dentistry , you can expect to come away with a completely natural-looking smile.</p>\n        <p>To consult with a leading cosmetic dentist in West Hollywood, give us a call at (323) 272-2388 or Contact us online for a consultation.</p>\n        <h2>Restore Your Smile’s Brilliance</h2>\n        <p>With your smile the best it’s ever looked, your confidence will be at an all-time high CONTACT EXQUISITE DENTISTRY (323) 272-2388 Call to schedule your cosmetic dentist appointment and experience true luxury.</p>\n        <h2>Who Are Hollywood Veneers For?</h2>\n        <p>If you’re thinking the best veneers in Hollywood are for patients with stained, discolored teeth, you’re absolutely correct. But there are several other excellent reasons to choose porcelain veneers: Your enamel is thin. In cases like this, you may be experiencing sensitivities to hot and cold. Your teeth may even look translucent. In these cases, a veneer will act as a protective shield to your teeth.</p>\n        <p>Your teeth are chipped or cracked.</p>\n        <p>Dental crowns are often used in situations where teeth are severely cracked, but occasionally that solution is not the best choice. For less extensive damage, dental veneers may be the perfect option. They’ll smooth out the surface of the tooth and make it look as good as new.</p>\n        <p>Your teeth have gaps between them. In certain cases, using veneers to fill the gaps between teeth is a quicker and easier choice that undergoing orthodontic work.</p>\n        <h2>Where Do I Get Hollywood Veneers?</h2>\n        <p>The best place to get your Hollywood-style veneers is… Hollywood! Work with Dr. Alexie Aguil of Exquisite Dentistry expert care in a truly relaxing and comfortable environment.</p>\n        <p>The offices of Exquisite Dentistry were the inspiration for the modern Dental Spa. From the moment you walk in the door, you’ll be greeted warmly by the personable team. The soothing sights and smells will put you at ease. When you’re invited into one of our comfortable chairs, you’ll be treated to a warm blanket and your choice of music or Netflix through noise-canceling headphones.</p>\n        <p>Get your porcelain veneers done at the Hollywood location that always treats you like a celebrity.</p>\n        <p>Contact us at (323) 272-2388 to set up your first appointment</p>\n      </div>",
