  "excerpt": "Porcelain veneers instantly brighten your smile by covering stained or discolored teeth with a thin, luminous shell.  Unlike whitening treatments that lighten natural enamel, veneers create a fresh surface that resists future staining from coffee, wine, or …",
  "content": "<div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n        <p>Porcelain veneers instantly brighten your smile by covering stained or discolored teeth with a thin, luminous shell. Unlike whitening treatments that lighten natural enamel, veneers create a fresh surface that resists future staining from coffee, wine, or aging.</p>\n        <p>Each veneer is custom shaped and shaded to match your features so the final result looks natural, not overdone. Veneers also smooth chips, fill small gaps, and even out tooth edges, giving you a polished, uniform smile in just a few visits.</p>\n        <p>With consistent brushing, flossing, and professional cleanings, veneers stay vibrant for many years. They are ideal if whitening alone cannot reach the shade you want or if you need to correct additional cosmetic concerns.</p>\n        <p>Curious whether veneers are right for you? Schedule a consultation. We will review your goals, show you sample shades, and design a personalized plan to give you the radiant, photo-ready smile you deserve.</p>\n        <p>Dental veneers are an effective treatment to design your smile exactly the way you want. They’re often used to help fix a chipped tooth, a gap between teeth, or even make a tiny adjustment to the bite of a person’s mouth.</p>\n        <p>For the best whitening benefits, nothing beats porcelain veneers . Unlike veneers of other types, they’re virtually indistinguishable from natural teeth. Porcelain veneers are expected to last 7-15 years, which means that with proper cleanings , your new smile can stay bright for a decade or more before they must be fixed or replaced.</p>\n        <h2>Veneers for Teeth Whitening at Exquisite Dentistry</h2>\n        <p>The veneers provided at Exquisite Dentistry are custom-made from the highest quality porcelain. Porcelain is a sturdy material that naturally resists stains and can be kept clean and bright with the same brushing and flossing that you are already doing on your normal teeth. As a result, veneer whitening refers to the visual impact that your new veneers will have on your smile.</p>\n        <h2>Restore Your Smile’s Brilliance</h2>\n        <p>With your smile the best it’s ever looked, your confidence will be at an all-time high CONTACT EXQUISITE DENTISTRY (323) 272-2388 Call to schedule your cosmetic dentist appointment and experience true luxury.</p>\n        <p>Patients who see Dr. Aguil about veneers and other cosmetic treatments can expect amazing customer service in the spa-like environment of Exquisite Dentistry. Dr. Aguil will work to ensure that the veneers they are fitted with will improve their smile and look just like their natural teeth. These porcelain veneers are manufactured by one of the premier dental labs in the United States. Once applied, your veneers will stay pristine and brilliant for year after year.</p>\n        <h2>Choosing Veneers for a Full and Brilliant Smile</h2>\n        <p>You have many options when designing your smile with porcelain veneers, and personalized care by an expert dentist can make all the difference. Dr. Aguil at Exquisite Dentistry will listen attentively to your goals and advise on aspects of treatment including the number of veneers applied, their shape, and matching their color to your teeth. We’ll work together to craft the perfect solution for you.</p>\n        <h2>Consult with Dr. Aguil About Your Porcelain Veneers</h2>\n        <p>To take the next step in brightening your smile, schedule your consultation at Exquisite Dentistry in West Hollywood. Give us a call at (323) 272-2388 .</p>\n      </div>",
